@node bugs_en "Known bugs"
Software:
· none

System:
· some programs (like ImageFX) make ENVArc: very big by storing their data
  in ENV:, which in  alternate mode is assigned  to ENVArc: (ENVArc:->ENV:
  option)

If you find any, let @{"me" link contact_en} know.
@endnode

